<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 12:16:01 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>2017 年伦敦格伦菲尔大厦火灾因英国政府失职造成 72 人死亡：调查</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/2017-grenfell-tower-fire-in-london-that-claimed-72-lives-due-to-uk-govt-failure-inquiry/articleshow/113061558.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113061558.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt; 2017 年伦敦格伦菲尔大厦火灾造成 72 人死亡，原因是政府、建筑行业和涉及安装易燃包层的公司的失误。一项公开调查批评当局和公司不诚实地宣传可燃包层是安全的。由于 2016 年翻修期间增加了包层，火势蔓延。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 10:18:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/2017-grenfell-tower-fire-in-london-that-claimed-72-lives-due-to-uk-govt-failure-inquiry/articleshow/113061558.cms</guid></item><item><title>中国警告学生警惕“漂亮”外国间谍</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/beware-of-beautiful-foreign-spies-china-warns-students/articleshow/113054344.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113054344.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;中国国家安全机构向有权接触敏感信息的学生发出警告，称外国间谍利用“浪漫陷阱”获取机密数据。据国家安全部称，这些间谍将自己伪装成有吸引力的人，以年轻学生为目标。建议市民对此类渗透方法保持警惕。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 06:57:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/beware-of-beautiful-foreign-spies-china-warns-students/articleshow/113054344.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国驻台湾特使宣称，在中国的军事威胁下，两国关系“坚如磐石”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-envoy-to-taiwan-declares-ties-rock-solid-amid-military-threats-from-china/articleshow/113061498.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113061498.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国驻台湾高级特使强调了美国对台湾坚定不移的支持，并强调提供大量军事援助和装备转让，以加强台湾对中国的防御。这一声明是在全球紧张局势加剧之际发表的，也是在美国和中国官员最近就维护两岸和平与稳定进行高层讨论之后发表的。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 10:16:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-envoy-to-taiwan-declares-ties-rock-solid-amid-military-threats-from-china/articleshow/113061498.cms</guid></item><item><title>日本岛屿消灭了杀死兔子的猫鼬</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/home/environment/flora-fauna/japanese-island-eradicates-rabbit-killing-mongoose/articleshow/113061173.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113061173.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;官员们表示，日本已经消灭了一座亚热带岛屿上的所有猫鼬，因为这些动物无视毒蛇，它们被带到这里来捕猎，并捕食濒临灭绝的当地兔子。当地官员告诉法新社：“据说，白天活跃的猫鼬很少与夜间活动的哈布蛇接触。”这种兔子只生活在奄美大岛和另一座岛屿上，被国际自然保护联盟（IUCN）红色名录列为濒危物种。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 10:07:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/home/environment/flora-fauna/japanese-island-eradicates-rabbit-killing-mongoose/articleshow/113061173.cms</guid></item><item><title>居民称博科圣地武装分子骑摩托车袭击尼日利亚村庄，造成 100 多人死亡</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/boko-haram-militants-on-motorcycles-attacked-a-nigerian-village-killing-over-100-residents-say/articleshow/113061165.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113061165.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;在尼日利亚东北部的约贝州，疑似博科圣地极端分子以市场和房屋为目标杀害了至少 100 名村民。据报道，死亡人数相互矛盾，社区领导人确认有 102 人死亡。蒂努布总统谴责了这次袭击，但没有采取新的安全措施来解决持续的暴力事件。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 10:07:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/boko-haram-militants-on-motorcycles-attacked-a-nigerian-village-killing-over-100-residents-say/articleshow/113061165.cms</guid></item><item><title>乌克兰外长德米特罗·库莱巴因重大改组而辞职</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/ukrainian-foreign-minister-dmytro-kuleba-resigns-amid-expected-major-reshuffle/articleshow/113059893.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113059893.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;俄罗斯袭击利沃夫后，乌克兰外交部长德米特罗·库莱巴在政府重大改组之前辞职。泽连斯基总统的目标是在访问美国之前加强政府实力。其他几位部长也相继辞职，标志着乌克兰政治格局发生重大变化。然而，库莱巴没有给出任何选择辞去外交部长职务的原因。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 09:58:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/ukrainian-foreign-minister-dmytro-kuleba-resigns-amid-expected-major-reshuffle/articleshow/113059893.cms</guid></item><item><title>联合国：工人在全球收入中所占份额急剧下降</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/workers-see-dramatic-fall-in-share-of-global-income-un/articleshow/113059967.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113059967.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;联合国国际劳工组织表示，自2004年以来，全球劳动收入份额下降了1.6%，导致每年工人短缺2.4万亿美元。这种下降因 Covid-19 大流行而加剧，凸显了不平等现象的加剧，并强调需要制定政策来确保公平的经济分配。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 09:36:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/workers-see-dramatic-fall-in-share-of-global-income-un/articleshow/113059967.cms</guid></item><item><title>计划于五月进行世界巡游的船舶在贝尔法斯特滞留了三个月</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/ship-scheduled-for-world-cruise-in-may-has-been-stranded-in-belfast-for-past-three-months/articleshow/113049474.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113049474.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;大约 200 名乘客滞留在贝尔法斯特，等待 Villa Vie Residences 的奥德赛 (Odyssey) 启航，开始为期三年的环球航行。这艘船于 1993 年建造，自 2020 年起停产，需要对其舵轴、钢结构和发动机进行维修。乘客可以在船上度过一天，但必须每天晚上离开。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 09:18:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/ship-scheduled-for-world-cruise-in-may-has-been-stranded-in-belfast-for-past-three-months/articleshow/113049474.cms</guid></item><item><title>特朗普声称，“如果当选，将公布不明飞行物录像和杰弗里·爱泼斯坦的文件”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/will-release-ufo-footage-jeffrey-epsteins-documents-if-elected-trump-claims/articleshow/113054792.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113054792.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;唐纳德·特朗普承诺，如果赢得总统选举，他将公布不明飞行物录像和杰弗里·爱泼斯坦的文件。他还打算就约翰·F·肯尼迪遇刺事件成立一个委员会，并在任期初期公开相关文件。特朗普澄清说，尽管他们相识，但他与爱泼斯坦没有任何关系。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 09:17:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/will-release-ufo-footage-jeffrey-epsteins-documents-if-elected-trump-claims/articleshow/113054792.cms</guid></item><item><title>伊朗因 Instagram 帖子支持 LGBTQIA+ 权利而召见澳大利亚大使</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/iran-summons-australian-ambassador-over-instagram-post-supporting-lgbtqia-rights/articleshow/113052673.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113052673.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;澳大利亚驻德黑兰大使馆在 Instagram 上发布了庆祝 LGBTQIA+ 青年“穿紫色日”的帖子后，伊朗召见了澳大利亚大使。伊朗批评该帖子宣扬同性恋并违背伊斯兰传统，而澳大利亚则捍卫其人权立场。该帖子仍可在大使馆的 Instagram 页面上查看。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 08:36:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/iran-summons-australian-ambassador-over-instagram-post-supporting-lgbtqia-rights/articleshow/113052673.cms</guid></item><item><title>“不要忽视我们”：哈马斯发布被杀以色列人质呼救的视频</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/do-not-neglect-us-hamas-releases-video-of-slain-israeli-hostage-calling-for-help/articleshow/113054612.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113054612.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;哈马斯发布了一段视频，显示奥里·达尼诺(Ori Danino)，他是在拉法被处决的六名人质之一。在视频中，达尼诺描述了恶劣的生活条件，并批评以色列领导层的救援尝试失败。他敦促以色列人继续努力拯救人质，并最后恳求“以色列人民：不要忽视我们。”</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 07:50:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/do-not-neglect-us-hamas-releases-video-of-slain-israeli-hostage-calling-for-help/articleshow/113054612.cms</guid></item><item><title>长岛男子被女友嫉妒的前夫杀害，葬礼上被铭记为“英雄”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/long-island-man-killed-by-girlfriends-jealous-ex-husband-remembered-as-hero-at-funeral/articleshow/113047008.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113047008.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt; 53 岁的长岛居民肯尼思·波尔曼 (Kenneth Pohlman) 是三个孩子的父亲，他在圣詹姆斯保护女友免受前夫伤害时被枪杀，后被安葬。哀悼者缅怀他作为父亲和体育爱好者的奉献精神。丹尼尔·科波拉曾对前妻凯莉·科波拉表现出虐待行为，现已被捕并承认杀人。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 06:14:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/long-island-man-killed-by-girlfriends-jealous-ex-husband-remembered-as-hero-at-funeral/articleshow/113047008.cms</guid></item><item><title>亨利是谁？世界上最年长的鳄鱼，与六位伴侣共产下 10,000 个孩子</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/who-is-henry-worlds-oldest-crocodile-who-has-fathered-10000-babies-with-six-partners/articleshow/113047554.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113047554.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;亨利是一条重 700 公斤、长 16 英尺的巨大尼罗河鳄鱼，现已正式成为世界上最古老的鳄鱼，享年 123 岁。他居住在南非的鳄鱼世界保护中心，已生育了 10,000 多个后代。 1903 年，亨利因捕食儿童而在博茨瓦纳被捕，如今他的生活已经远离了他的暴力过去。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 06:10:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/who-is-henry-worlds-oldest-crocodile-who-has-fathered-10000-babies-with-six-partners/articleshow/113047554.cms</guid></item><item><title>官员称，数千罗兴亚人因缅甸暴力事件逃往孟加拉国</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/thousands-of-rohingya-flee-to-bangladesh-from-violence-in-myanmar-official-says/articleshow/113052570.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113052570.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;最近，约有 8,000 名罗兴亚穆斯林越境进入孟加拉国，逃离缅甸若开邦不断升级的暴力局势。孟加拉国官员报告说，该国难民负担已经过重，无法容纳更多难民。政府计划就这场危机进行紧急讨论，并敦促国际社会采取行动，制止缅甸持续发生的暴力事件。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 06:08:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/thousands-of-rohingya-flee-to-bangladesh-from-violence-in-myanmar-official-says/articleshow/113052570.cms</guid></item><item><title>德国极右翼德国选择党的崛起引发了集中营所在地的恐惧</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/rise-of-germanys-far-right-afd-stokes-fears-at-concentration-camp-site/articleshow/113052167.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113052167.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;负责监督德国布痕瓦尔德集中营纪念馆的历史学家对极右翼选择党在图林根州选举中获胜后不断上升的威胁感到震惊。他预计反移民情绪将会增加，纪念馆的预算可能会被削减，该纪念馆纪念了超过 56,000 名纳粹罪行的受害者。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 05:51:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/rise-of-germanys-far-right-afd-stokes-fears-at-concentration-camp-site/articleshow/113052167.cms</guid></item><item><title>观看：巴基斯坦飞行员在起飞前倾身清洁飞机窗户</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/watch-pilot-leans-over-cleans-window-of-aircraft-before-take-off-in-pakistan/articleshow/113058162.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113058162.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;据记录，一名 Serene Air 飞行员在起飞前从外部清洁了一架空客 A330-200 的挡风玻璃。等待登机的乘客在视频中捕捉到了这一时刻，该视频随后在网上疯传。人们的反应多种多样，从嘲笑到为这种在车辆操作员中很常见的做法辩护。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 09:55:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/watch-pilot-leans-over-cleans-window-of-aircraft-before-take-off-in-pakistan/articleshow/113058162.cms</guid></item><item><title>空中交通管制员被发现睡着后，澳大利亚政府将制定新规定</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/australian-government-to-enact-new-regulations-after-air-traffic-controller-found-asleep/articleshow/113051080.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113051080.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt; 2022 年 12 月 9 日，一名空中交通管制员被发现在布里斯班空中交通服务中心值班期间打瞌睡，澳大利亚运输安全局颁布了新规定。一项调查揭示了疲劳管理实践中的重大问题。作为回应，澳大利亚航空服务公司增加了人员配备并更新了疲劳评估工具，以防止再次发生此类事件。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 05:25:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/australian-government-to-enact-new-regulations-after-air-traffic-controller-found-asleep/articleshow/113051080.cms</guid></item><item><title>复仇心切的泰国跨性别女人十多年来诈骗了 70 多名日本男人</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/vengeful-thai-trans-woman-scams-over-70-japanese-men-for-over-a-decade/articleshow/113049690.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113049690.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;一名名叫艾米的泰国变性女子在13年时间里诈骗了70多名日本男子近3000万泰铢。被日本男友抛弃后，她开始向日本男人复仇。她冒充来自台湾或香港的游客来博取同情并操纵男人。她于8月4日在曼谷被捕。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 04:57:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/vengeful-thai-trans-woman-scams-over-70-japanese-men-for-over-a-decade/articleshow/113049690.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴基斯坦政府禁止公务员未经许可使用社交媒体</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-government-bars-public-servants-from-using-social-media-without-permission/articleshow/113050217.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113050217.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;巴基斯坦政府已限制所有政府雇员未经事先许可使用社交媒体，以防止官方信息泄露。禁止员工分享可能影响政府声誉、政策或国家主权的意见或文件。机构必须监控社交媒体是否存在任何令人反感的内容。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 04:44:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-government-bars-public-servants-from-using-social-media-without-permission/articleshow/113050217.cms</guid></item><item><title>哈里王子会重返王室职责吗？苏塞克斯公爵澄清</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/is-prince-harry-returning-to-royal-duties-duke-of-sussex-clarifies/articleshow/113049040.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113049040.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;哈里王子似乎对恢复王室职责不感兴趣，并与好朋友定居在加利福尼亚州。尽管有传言称他会回国，但由于他目前在美国的处境并不理想，他还是向老熟人寻求建议。他计划在联合国大会高级别周期间前往纽约进行慈善工作。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 04:16:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/is-prince-harry-returning-to-royal-duties-duke-of-sussex-clarifies/articleshow/113049040.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>